#

Herb Roasted Potatoes

40 min
$5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodSide Dish

Description

Flavorful roasted potatoes with a crispy exterior and fluffy interior, seasoned to perfection.

Ingredients

  • baby potatoes: 2 pounds
  • olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • dried rosemary: 1 teaspoon
  • dried thyme: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
